# STM32 + Keil MDK project

# Keil user/session files (do not affect project source)
*.uvoptx
*.uvguix.*
*.uvgui.*
*.uvtmp

# Keil build output directories
**/Objects/
**/Listings/

# Keil/CMSIS generated RTE target folders
**/RTE/_Target_*/

